  <Typography.Body className="font-semibold">Item Title</Typography.Body>
  <Typography.Small variant="secondary">Subtitle</Typography.Small>
</View>
```

## üöÄ Quick Checklist

1. Import from `@/shared/components/Typography`
2. Choose correct component (H1-H6, Body, Label, etc.)
3. Use `variant` for colors, not hardcoded values
4. Use `className` for spacing/alignment, not `style`
5. Add `mb-` classes for vertical rhythm

